                    <div class="title-wrapper">
                        <h2>Contractor Membership Plans</h2>
                        <p>Please choose the best membership plan for you.</p>
                        <p class="disclaimer">All plans are based on one year memberships.</p>
                        <p class="disclaimer">There is a 1 time fee of $99 to verify your compan is a DBA, LLC, or INC</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card-wrapper">
                        <div class="title-wrapper">
                            <h3>Basic Plan</h3>
                            <p>Best plan for those companies that want to stay small and local.</p>
                            <s><p>$324<span class="disclaimer"> per year</p></s>
                            <p class="promo-price">$96<span class="disclaimer"> per year</span></p>
                            <p class="disclaimer">That's less than $0.27 per day!</p>
                            <button onclick="UpgradeToBronzeSubscription()">@BuyNowBronze</button>
                            <div class="card-meta">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Company is Listed in 1 Contractor Category</li>
                                    <li>Company is Listed in 10 Zip Codes</li>
                                    <li>Unlimited category searches</li>
                                    <li>Unlimited zip code searches</li>
                                    <li>Listed in Prohz directory</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
